				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Switching Macro?<a name="15318"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 12 04 5:45 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Instrument (or any gear of Inventory stuff) swapping MUST be done with the mouse.  That means that with one hand you twist songs, with your second hand you navigate, and with your THIRD hand you swap.
<br />

<br />
Honestly, the only time you can effectively instrument swap, unless you are VERY talented indeed, is when you are in a group, or some situation where you do not need to move very much.  (AE twisting resists and mana on a raid is another good example).
<br />

<br />
Klapton</span></td>
